{"id":964,"date":"2022-09-05T15:58:20","date_gmt":"2022-09-05T15:58:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/?post_type=docs&#038;p=964"},"modified":"2023-04-20T11:31:56","modified_gmt":"2023-04-20T11:31:56","slug":"what-is-metamask","status":"publish","type":"docs","link":"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/docs\/what-is-metamask\/","title":{"rendered":"What is Metamask"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"478\" src=\"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask.jpg\" alt=\"What is MetaMask\" class=\"wp-image-1415\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-300x140.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-600x280.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-768x359.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"is-style-info coblocks-alert-paragraph\">MetaMask is a cryptocurrency wallet that enables users to access the Web 3 ecosystem of decentralized applications (dapps).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What is MetaMask?<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Most cryptocurrency users only have wallets linked to the exchanges on which they trade. It resembles a typical email\/password log which gives people the erroneous notion of how blockchain addresses function.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/metamask.io\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">MetaMask<\/a><\/strong> is a non-custodial wallet that can be accessed from your browser or mobile and it provides you with complete control over your assets. It has significant advantages and disadvantages, which we shall discuss below.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In short, MetaMask is a cryptocurrency wallet that allows you to store, transfer and trade <strong>ERC-20 tokens<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>What distinguishes <strong>MetaMask<\/strong> from other wallet applications is its ability to interface with smart contract-based platforms that are live on <strong>Ethereum<\/strong> or Layer2s on Ethereum.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, if you go to Alchemix and decide to stake your tokens for profit or go to OpenSea to look at new NFTs, you need to link your MetaMask wallet to complete the transactions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Of course, many alternative wallets function, but MetaMask is the most popular because it is completely open-source.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-medium-font-size is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"What is MetaMask?\" width=\"1778\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/YVgfHZMFFFQ?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to get started using MetaMask<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Though it might seem complicated to beginners, MetaMask is one of the simpler Ethereum wallets and dapp browsers to use, and can be set up in a couple of minutes in most cases.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To use MetaMask, you will need either <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/chrome\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Chrome<\/a><\/strong>, a Chromium-based browser such as <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/brave.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Brave<\/a><\/strong>, or <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.mozilla.org\/en-US\/firefox\/new\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Firefox<\/a><\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-medium-font-size is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Getting Started with MetaMask\" width=\"1778\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/GNPz-Dv5BjM?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Step 1: Install MetaMask<\/strong><\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>First, you\u2019ll need to download and install the official Metamask extension (also known as a plugin or add-on) for your chosen browser. For most people, this is the <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/chrome.google.com\/webstore\/detail\/metamask\/nkbihfbeogaeaoehlefnkodbefgpgknn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Google Chrome extension<\/a><\/strong> or the <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/addons.mozilla.org\/en-US\/firefox\/addon\/ether-metamask\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Firefox addon<\/a><\/strong>. For our guide, we\u2019ll be using the Firefox version, but the steps are nearly identical for other browsers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once installed, you should see the below splash screen. Click the &#8220;Get Started&#8221; button to begin creating your Ethereum wallet using MetaMask.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-1.jpg\" alt=\"metamask\" class=\"wp-image-8615\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-1.jpg 500w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-1-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Step 2: Create a Wallet<\/strong><\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-3 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-2-1.jpg\" alt=\"What is MetaMask\" class=\"wp-image-1404\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-2-1.jpg 500w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-2-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-2-1-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-2-1-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-3-1.jpg\" alt=\"What is MetaMask\" class=\"wp-image-1405\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-3-1.jpg 500w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-3-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-3-1-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-3-1-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You\u2019ll then be asked if you want to help improve MetaMask. Click \u2018No Thanks\u2019 if this doesn\u2019t interest you, otherwise click <strong>\u2018I agree\u2019.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>On the next step, click the \u2018Create a Wallet\u2019 button.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-4.jpg\" alt=\"What is MetaMask\" class=\"wp-image-1403\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-4.jpg 500w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-4-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-4-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-4-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pick a password on the next step. This needs to be at least 8 characters long. We recommend using a completely unique password that hasn\u2019t been used anywhere else, and one that contains a mixture of upper and lower case letters, symbols, and numbers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Read and accept the Terms of Use, and click \u2018Create\u2019 once your password has been set.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>MetaMask will then present you with your 12-word backup phrase. You\u2019ll need to write this phrase down carefully, with the words recorded in the same order displayed on your screen. This phrase will be needed to recover your wallet should you ever lose access to your computer, and should be kept stored somewhere safe. Anybody who has access to your 12-word backup phrase will have access to the funds in your MetaMask wallet, so keep it private.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Click <strong>\u2018Next\u2019<\/strong> once you\u2019ve written this down.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-4 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-5.jpg\" alt=\"What is MetaMask\" class=\"wp-image-1408\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-5.jpg 500w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-5-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-5-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-5-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-6.jpg\" alt=\"What is MetaMask\" class=\"wp-image-1409\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-6.jpg 500w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-6-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-6-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-6-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Confirm your backup phrase on the next screen by entering the words in the same order saved previously. Click <strong>\u2018Confirm\u2019<\/strong> once done.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You have now almost completed the MetaMask setup process. Just click <strong>&#8216;All Done<\/strong>&#8216; on the final page, and you will be automatically logged in to MetaMask.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-background\" style=\"background-color:#fdf5d9\">\ud83d\udce3 If you ever get logged out, you\u2019ll be able to log back in again by clicking the MetaMask icon, which will have been added to your web browser (usually found next to the URL bar).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Step 3: Make a deposit<\/strong><\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-7.jpg\" alt=\"What is MetaMask\" class=\"wp-image-1410\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-7.jpg 500w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-7-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-7-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/metamask-7-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Select view account.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>You may now view and share your public address with others. MetaMask provides certain options for purchasing coins, but you may also do it differently; all you need is your wallet address.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>\ud83d\udca1 The MetaMask extension will always be there on your browser\u2019s extension bar.<\/code><\/pre>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>MetaMask is a cryptocurrency wallet that enables users to access the Web 3 ecosystem of decentralized applications (dapps). What is MetaMask? Most cryptocurrency users only have wallets linked to the exchanges on which they trade. It resembles a typical email\/password log which gives people the erroneous notion of how blockchain addresses function. MetaMask is a non-custodial wallet that can be accessed from your browser or mobile and it provides you with complete control over your assets. It has significant advantages and disadvantages, which we shall discuss below. In short, MetaMask is a cryptocurrency wallet that allows you to store, transfer\u2026<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_coblocks_attr":"","_coblocks_dimensions":"","_coblocks_responsive_height":"","_coblocks_accordion_ie_support":"","_uag_custom_page_level_css":""},"doc_category":[9],"doc_tag":[],"blocksy_meta":{"styles_descriptor":{"styles":{"desktop":"","tablet":"","mobile":""},"google_fonts":[],"version":5}},"uagb_featured_image_src":{"full":false,"thumbnail":false,"medium":false,"medium_large":false,"large":false,"1536x1536":false,"2048x2048":false},"uagb_author_info":{"display_name":"smartnft","author_link":"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/author\/smartnft\/"},"uagb_comment_info":0,"uagb_excerpt":"MetaMask is a cryptocurrency wallet that enables users to access the Web 3 ecosystem of decentralized applications (dapps). What is MetaMask? Most cryptocurrency users only have wallets linked to the exchanges on which they trade. It resembles a typical email\/password log which gives people the erroneous notion of how blockchain addresses function. MetaMask is a&hellip;","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/docs\/964"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/docs"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/docs"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=964"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/docs\/964\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=964"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"doc_category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/doc_category?post=964"},{"taxonomy":"doc_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wpsmartnft.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/doc_tag?post=964"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}